      "content": "- **Core scaffold:** short **peptidic/peptidomimetic chain** (three amino-acid-like units).\n- **Functional groups:**\n  - **Three amide NHs** (\u2013NH\u2013C(=O)\u2013): H-bond donors/acceptors, but **non-basic** (amide N is not protonatable at pH 7.4).\n  - **One terminal carbamate/ester-like group**: `NC(=O)OCH2\u2013` (carbamate carbonyl + ether oxygen).\n- **Hydrophobic features:**\n  - Multiple **isobutyl side chains** (Leu-like; strongly lipophilic).\n  - One **phenyl ring** (benzyl carbamate): aromatic lipophilicity.\n- **Basic nitrogens / CYP2D6 \u201canchor\u201d:** **none** (all nitrogens are amide nitrogens).\n- **Structural alerts for CYP2D6 inhibition:** typical alerts are **tertiary amines / protonatable basic centers** and \u201cquinidine-like\u201d motifs; this molecule lacks those.",
